.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/110%2c%e9%87%91%e8%a8%b4%2c420%2c20220412%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,110,金訴,420,20220412,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"金訴","JNO":"420","JDATE":"20220412","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}